-- Euro Extends Gain Against Dollar on Speculation ECB May Buy Debt
-- B y   K e n n e t h   P r i n g l e
-- 2012-06-01T13:59:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-01/euro-extends-gain-against-dollar-on-speculation-ecb-may-buy-debt.html
The euro extended a gain against the
dollar as Spanish and Italian government bonds advanced on
speculation the European Central Bank may purchase the
securities to stem an increase in borrowing costs. The euro rose
0.2 percent to $1.2395 at 9:58 a.m. in  New York   To contact the reporter on this story:
